Run the following in a terminal:

mkdir <PROJECT>
cd <PROJECT>
virtualenv env-<CURRENT DATE>
ln -s env-<CURRENT DATE> env
source env/bin/activate
git clone git@github.com:concentricsky/csky-django-template.git code
pip install -r code/requirements.txt
cp code/apps/mainsite/settings_local.py.example code/apps/mainsite/settings_local.py

Edit the settings_local.py file and insert local credentials for DATABASES, then run the following:

code/manage.py migrate
